  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2–8 Player Local PvP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with or against friends in a fast-paced platform fighter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>21,000+ Cosmetic Combinations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/ce9f7d718ad90689e88e3a93e096e531.poster.avif?t=1774233882\" width=290 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/ce9f7d718ad90689e88e3a93e096e531.webm?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/ce9f7d718ad90689e88e3a93e096e531.mp4?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>17 Guns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0cdb86cd9aeb45518a826995e601b8d1.poster.avif?t=1774233882\" width=290 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0cdb86cd9aeb45518a826995e601b8d1.webm?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0cdb86cd9aeb45518a826995e601b8d1.mp4?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>5 Special Attacks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/962205d85d0e47e5b18d52e624e50b49.poster.avif?t=1774233882\" width=612 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/962205d85d0e47e5b18d52e624e50b49.webm?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/962205d85d0e47e5b18d52e624e50b49.mp4?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>6 Unique Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0d1f78e20221c4e7309c74bcb60b2601.poster.avif?t=1774233882\" width=580 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0d1f78e20221c4e7309c74bcb60b2601.webm?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/0d1f78e20221c4e7309c74bcb60b2601.mp4?t=1774233882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 Game Modes · 35 Levels</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deathmatch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >King of the Crown</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower Control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basketball</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Movement-Focused Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll to gain speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269830/extras/87e1cb4311a29af67ea7387abd3eb59a.poster.avif?t=1774233882\" width=556 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3